Adding elements to array in by-reference foreach
-----
<?php
foreach ($a as &$b) {
    $a[] = $c;
}

-----
Possible adding to array on the last iteration of a by-reference foreach loop
-----
<?php
foreach ($a as $k => &$b) {
    $a[] = $c;
}

-----
Possible adding to array on the last iteration of a by-reference foreach loop
-----
<?php
foreach ($a as $b) {
    $a[] = $c;
}
